                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nObesity is defined as an increase in body weight beyond the body’s physical requirements that results in an abnormal accumulation of fat cells. Exercise that incorporates 150 minutes of moderate-intensity aerobic activity with muscle-strengthening activities 2 or more days per week is recommended. Therefore, option 3 is correct.",
